'''山茶属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Camellia''}}），或稱'''茶屬'''，是[[山茶科|山茶科]]的一大属。品種約有150種。主要分布[[中國|中國]]的[[長江|長江]]以南至[[雲南|雲南]]及[[越南|越南]]一帶的地區，在東亞與[[東南亞|東南亞]]地區也有分布。其中的[[茶樹|茶樹]]產[[茶葉|茶葉]]，許多种也可以做觀賞植物<ref>{{cite book|title=RHS A-Z encyclopedia of garden plants|url=https://archive.org/details/azencyclopediaof0000unse|year=2008|publisher=Dorling Kindersley|location=United Kingdom|isbn=1405332964|page=1136}}</ref>。

属名''Camellia''为纪念捷克旅行家George Joseph Camell（1667-1706）而命名。

[[File:Camellia_japonica_MHNT.BOT.2010.13.3.jpg|thumb]]木横切面]]

== 物種 ==
約有100 ~ 250 種，包括：

# [[金花茶|金花茶]] -''Camellia nitissima''
# [[山茶花|山茶花]] - ''Camellia japonica'' <small>L., 1753</small>
# [[茶樹|茶樹]]（[[茶|茶]]） - ''Camellia sinensis'' <small>(L.) Kuntze, 1887</small>
## [[台灣山茶|台灣山茶]] - ''Camellia sinensis'' f. ''formosensis''
## [[阿薩姆茶|阿薩姆茶]] - ''Camellia sinensis'' var. ''assamica'' <small>(J.W. Mast.) Kitam., 1950</small>
## [[香花茶|香花茶]] - ''Camellia sinensis var. waldenae''
# [[茶梅|茶梅]] - ''Camellia sasanqua'' <small>Thunb., 1784</small>
# [[油茶|油茶]] - ''Camellia oleifera'' <small>Abel, 1818</small>
# [[柠檬金花茶|柠檬金花茶]] -''Camellia limonia''
# [[大理茶|大理茶]] -''Camellia taliensis''
# [[大苞茶|大苞茶]] -''Camellia grandibracteata''
# [[大果红山茶|大果红山茶]] -''Camellia magnocarpa''
# [[榕江茶|榕江茶]] -''Camellia yungkiangensis''
# [[唐山茶|唐山茶]] - ''Camellia reticulata'' <small>Lindl., 1827</small>
# [[柳葉山茶|柳葉山茶]] - ''Camellia salicifolia'' <small>Champ. ex Benth., 1851</small>
# [[細葉山茶|細葉山茶]] - ''Camellia tenuifolia''
# [[阿里山茶|阿里山茶]] - ''Camellia transarisanensis'' <small>(Hayata) Cohen-Stuart, 1919</small>
# [[泛能高山茶|泛能高山茶]] - ''Camellia transnokoensis'' <small>Hayata, 1919</small>
# [[短柱山茶|短柱山茶]] - ''Camellia brevistyla'' <small>(Hayata) Cohen-Stuart, 1916</small>
# [[尾葉山茶|尾葉山茶]] - ''Camellia caudata'' <small>Wall., 1832</small>
# [[垢果山茶|垢果山茶]] - ''Camellia furfuracea'' <small>(Merr.) Cohen-Stuart, 1919</small>
# [[恆春山茶|恆春山茶]] - ''Camellia hengchunensis''
# [[能高山茶|能高山茶]] - ''Camellia nokoensis'' <small>Hayata, 1919</small>
#[[香港茶|香港茶]] - ''Camellia hongkongensis'' [[Seem.|Seem.]] (1859)
#[[葛量洪茶|葛量洪茶]] - ''Camellia granthamiana'' [[Joseph_Robert_Sealy|Sealy]], J. Roy. Hort. Soc. 81(4): 182. 1956.

